---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="What We Treat â€” Southern Winds Hospital" hideFooterCta>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg">
      <img src="/images/treatment-hero.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" />
    </div>
    <div class="page-hero__diagonal"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__curve"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__inner">
      <div class="page-hero__content">
        <h1 class="page-hero__heading">What We Treat</h1>
        <nav class="page-hero__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <span>/</span>
          <span aria-current="page">What We Treat</span>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="intro__inner">
      <h2 class="intro__heading">Treatment</h2>
      <div class="intro__content">
        <p>At Southern Winds Hospital, we are experts in the treatment of mental health disorders and addictions. We are licensed to offer assistance for multiple types of disorders. With an emphasis on the therapeutic process, we focus on getting to know the patient and working with each individual's skills and strengths. In this way, we compassionately and efficiently move forward in the recovery process.</p>
        <p>Based on our philosophy of <strong>"treating the patient and not only their diagnosis,"</strong> we take each case as a unique opportunity to help a person make progress during an adverse situation. Our therapy process is personalized with care for each individual.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mental-health-section">
    <div class="mental-health-section__inner">
      <div class="mental-health-section__content">
        <h2 class="mental-health-section__heading">Mental Health Disorders</h2>
        <div class="mental-health-section__stat">
          <span class="mental-health-section__stat-number">43.8M</span>
          <span class="mental-health-section__stat-text">adults experience some type of mental health problem each year</span>
        </div>
        <p>These disorders cause problems in the way in which an individual relates to the environment. We provide assistance to those who deal with mental health problems and disorders.</p>
        <p>A mental health disorder is an alteration of emotional, cognitive, or behavioral capacity in which basic psychological processes are affected. Its main consequence is that it hinders the interaction and adaptation of the individual with the environment.</p>
        <p>At Southern Winds Hospital, we know how difficult it is to deal with mental health disorders, and that is why we offer psychiatric help to different types of disorders, always focusing on the therapeutic process.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mental-health-section__image">
        <img src="/images/mental-health.jpg" alt="Compassionate mental health care" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="disorders-section">
    <div class="disorders-section__inner">
      <h2 class="disorders-section__heading">Disorders We Treat</h2>
      <p class="disorders-section__subtext">Our experienced team provides comprehensive treatment for a wide range of mental health conditions.</p>
      
      <div class="disorders-grid">
        <div class="disorder-card">
          <div class="disorder-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 15h8"/><path d="M9 9h.01"/><path d="M15 9h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="disorder-card__title">Mood Disorders</h3>
          <ul class="disorder-card__list">
            <li>Bipolar Disorder</li>
            <li>Depression</li>
            <li>Dual Diagnosis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="disorder-card">
          <div class="disorder-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="disorder-card__title">Personality Disorders</h3>
          <ul class="disorder-card__list">
            <li>Borderline Personality Disorder</li>
            <li>Dependent Personality Disorder</li>
            <li>Histrionic Personality Disorder</li>
            <li>Narcissistic Personality Disorder</li>
            <li>Multiple Personality Disorder</li>
            <li>Avoidance Disorder</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="disorder-card">
          <div class="disorder-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="disorder-card__title">Anxiety & Stress</h3>
          <ul class="disorder-card__list">
            <li>Panic Disorder</li>
            <li>Phobia</li>
            <li>Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD)</li>
            <li>Trauma</li>
            <li>Obsessive Compulsive Disorder</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="disorder-card">
          <div class="disorder-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="disorder-card__title">Behavioral & Crisis</h3>
          <ul class="disorder-card__list">
            <li>Suicidal Ideations</li>
            <li>Homicidal Ideation Disorder</li>
            <li>Poor Impulse Control</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="disorder-card">
          <div class="disorder-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10H12V2z"/><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 10 10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="disorder-card__title">Psychotic Disorders</h3>
          <ul class="disorder-card__list">
            <li>Schizophrenia</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="disorder-card">
          <div class="disorder-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="disorder-card__title">Other Conditions</h3>
          <ul class="disorder-card__list">
            <li>Eating Disorders</li>
            <li>Pain Management</li>
            <li>Personality Disorders</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="help-section">
    <div class="help-section__inner">
      <div class="help-section__image">
        <img src="/images/how-we-help.jpg" alt="Therapy session at Southern Winds Hospital" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="help-section__content">
        <h2 class="help-section__heading">How Can We Help You?</h2>
        <p>At Southern Winds, we have professionals in the treatment of addictions that guide the patient during all stages of the process and ensure that rehabilitation is done in a healthy way, respecting the patient and his ability to react to therapy.</p>
        <p>In addition, we provide psychological and emotional assistance, through an accompaniment and follow-up process where we take care that the progress achieved is maintained over time and benefits the patient's life.</p>
        <div class="help-section__features">
          <div class="help-section__feature">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Personalized treatment plans</span>
          </div>
          <div class="help-section__feature">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Ongoing support & follow-up</span>
          </div>
          <div class="help-section__feature">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Experienced professionals</span>
          </div>
          <div class="help-section__feature">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Compassionate care</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="help-section__btn">
          Get Started Today
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-section__inner">
      <h2 class="cta-section__heading">Ready to Start Your Recovery?</h2>
      <p class="cta-section__text">Our team is here to help you take the first step toward healing.</p>
      <div class="cta-section__actions">
        <a href="tel:7868267552" class="cta-section__btn cta-section__btn--primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
          Call (786) 826-7552
        </a>
        <a href="/admissions" class="cta-section__btn cta-section__btn--secondary">Learn About Admissions</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../styles/partials/variables' as *;
  @use '../styles/partials/mixins' as *;

  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 220px;
    overflow: hidden;

    @include respond(md) {
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    &__bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 1;

      img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      &::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba($color-primary, 0.75);
      }
    }

    &__diagonal {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 60%;
      height: 100%;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 70% 100%, 0 100%);
      z-index: 2;

      @include respond(md) {
        width: 50%;
        clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 65% 100%, 0 100%);
      }
    }

    &__curve {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -1px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 50px;
      background: $color-white;
      z-index: 4;
      clip-path: ellipse(45% 100% at 50% 100%);

      @include respond(md) {
        height: 70px;
        clip-path: ellipse(45% 100% at 50% 100%);
      }
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      padding-block: $space-2xl;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;

      @include respond(lg) {
        padding-block: $space-3xl;
      }
    }

    &__content {
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-white;
      margin-bottom: $space-xs;

      &::after {
        content: '';
        display: block;
        width: 48px;
        height: 3px;
        background-color: $color-white;
        margin-top: $space-xs;
      }

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-3xl;
      }
    }

    &__breadcrumb {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: $space-xs;
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      color: rgba($color-white, 0.85);
      margin-top: $space-xs;

      a {
        color: rgba($color-white, 0.85);
        transition: color $transition-fast;

        &:hover {
          color: $color-white;
        }
      }

      span[aria-current] {
        color: $color-white;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
    }
  }

  .intro {
    background: $color-white;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;
    padding-top: $space-lg;

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-navy;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: $space-lg;

      &::after {
        content: '';
        display: block;
        width: 48px;
        height: 3px;
        background: $color-primary;
        margin: $space-sm auto 0;
      }
    }

    &__content {
      p {
        font-family: $font-body;
        font-size: $fs-sm;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: $color-text-muted;
        margin-bottom: $space-md;
        text-align: center;

        &:last-child {
          margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        @include respond(md) {
          font-size: $fs-base;
        }

        strong {
          color: $color-primary;
          font-weight: 600;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .mental-health-section {
    background: $color-primary;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;

    @include respond(lg) {
      padding-block: $space-3xl;
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: $space-xl;
      align-items: center;

      @include respond(lg) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    &__content {
      color: $color-white;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: $space-md;

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-3xl;
      }
    }

    &__stat {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: $space-md;
      padding: $space-md;
      background: rgba($color-white, 0.1);
      border-radius: $radius-md;
      margin-bottom: $space-lg;
    }

    &__stat-number {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-3xl;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: $color-white;
      line-height: 1;

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-4xl;
      }
    }

    &__stat-text {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      color: rgba($color-white, 0.9);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    p {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba($color-white, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: $space-md;

      &:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
    }

    &__image {
      border-radius: $radius-lg;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: $shadow-xl;

      img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      }
    }
  }

  .disorders-section {
    background: $color-offwhite;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;

    @include respond(lg) {
      padding-block: $space-3xl;
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-navy;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: $space-xs;
    }

    &__subtext {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      color: $color-text-muted;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: $space-xl;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }

  .disorders-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: $space-md;

    @include respond(sm) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    @include respond(lg) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .disorder-card {
    background: $color-white;
    padding: $space-lg;
    border-radius: $radius-md;
    border: 1px solid $color-border;
    transition: all $transition-base;

    &:hover {
      border-color: transparent;
      box-shadow: $shadow-lg;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    &__icon {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba($color-primary, 0.08), rgba($color-primary, 0.15));
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: $color-primary;
      margin-bottom: $space-sm;
    }

    &__title {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-lg;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-navy;
      margin-bottom: $space-sm;
    }

    &__list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;

      li {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: $space-md;
        font-family: $font-body;
        font-size: $fs-sm;
        color: $color-text-muted;
        margin-bottom: $space-xs;
        line-height: 1.5;

        &::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          left: 0;
          top: 8px;
          width: 6px;
          height: 6px;
          background: $color-primary;
          border-radius: 50%;
        }

        &:last-child {
          margin-bottom: 0;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .help-section {
    background: $color-white;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;

    @include respond(lg) {
      padding-block: $space-3xl;
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: $space-xl;
      align-items: center;

      @include respond(lg) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    &__image {
      border-radius: $radius-lg;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: $shadow-xl;
      order: 2;

      @include respond(lg) {
        order: 1;
      }

      img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      }
    }

    &__content {
      order: 1;

      @include respond(lg) {
        order: 2;
      }
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-navy;
      margin-bottom: $space-md;
    }

    p {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: $color-text-muted;
      margin-bottom: $space-md;
    }

    &__features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: $space-xs;
      margin-bottom: $space-lg;

      @include respond(sm) {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    &__feature {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: $space-xs;
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      color: $color-text;

      svg {
        color: $color-primary;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
    }

    &__btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: $space-xs;
      padding: $space-sm $space-lg;
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: $color-white;
      background: $color-primary;
      border-radius: $radius-sm;
      transition: all $transition-base;

      &:hover {
        background: $color-primary-dark;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba($color-primary, 0.3);
        gap: $space-sm;
      }
    }
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba($color-primary-dark, 0.52), rgba($color-primary, 0.88)), url('/images/waves.png') center / cover no-repeat;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;

    @include respond(lg) {
      padding-block: $space-3xl;
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-white;
      margin-bottom: $space-xs;

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-3xl;
      }
    }

    &__text {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      color: rgba($color-white, 0.85);
      margin-bottom: $space-lg;

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-base;
      }
    }

    &__actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: $space-sm;
    }

    &__btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: $space-xs;
      padding: $space-sm $space-xl;
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: $radius-sm;
      transition: all $transition-base;

      &--primary {
        color: $color-primary;
        background-color: $color-white;

        &:hover {
          transform: translateY(-2px);
          box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
      }

      &--secondary {
        color: $color-white;
        background: transparent;
        border: 2px solid $color-white;

        &:hover {
          background: $color-white;
          color: $color-primary;
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>